# Mantine Component Documentation

When implementing or modifying a component and the correct Mantine API usage isn't obvious, look up the relevant Mantine docs before writing code.

Docs follow this URL pattern: `https://mantine.dev/core/{component-name}/`

Examples:
- TextInput → https://mantine.dev/core/text-input/
- Modal → https://mantine.dev/core/modal/
- Button → https://mantine.dev/core/button/
- Select → https://mantine.dev/core/select/
- Stack → https://mantine.dev/core/stack/

Use the `WebFetch` tool to pull the docs page when you need to verify props, Styles API selectors, or usage patterns you're unsure about.
